A [[currency_exchange]] with a BTC/USD market for trading between USD (U.S. Dollars) against bitcoins.  The site has Russian and English user interface translations.

The methods allowed for adding funds to an account are [[Liberty_Reserve]], Webmoney WMZ, Interkassa.com and their own BTC-E redeem codes.  The withdrawal methods are Webmoney WMZ, [[Liberty_Reserve]], QIWI, LiqPAY and BTC-E redeem code. BTC-E redeem codes exchange provided by [[AurumXchange]].

##History

The site was first announced on July 17, 2011 (2.1) with test mode trading.  Live trading began on August 7, 2011 (2.2).

